<TITLE>
Tolba the Turtle (Dolba, Doleba, Toba)
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Information and legends about the Native American mythological figure Tolba (Dolba),
a legendary turtle who carried the earth on his back according to Abenaki mythology.">
<meta charset="utf-8"/> 				

